     <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12 clearfix page-wrapper">
       <div class="row">
        <main class=" col-sm-12" id="maincontent" role="main">
         <div id="departmentheader">
          <h2>
           Mission Statement
          </h2>
         </div>
         <p>
          The
          <strong>
           Spatial Sciences Center's
          </strong>
          (SSC) mission is to (1) promote and support basic and applied research incorporating
                              geographic information science, remote sensing, global positioning system, and spatial
                              analysis, (2) support and facilitate undergraduate and graduate courses in spatial
                              sciences offered through departments within the MSU, and (3) promote the application
                              of spatial sciences throughout MSU through outreach to faculty and staff.
         </p>
         <p>
          <strong>
           Announcements:
          </strong>
         </p>
         <ul>
          <li>
           <strong>
            <a href="http://landresources.montana.edu/dept/faculty/powell-s.html">
             Scott Powell
            </a>
           </strong>
           , Assistant Professor of Environmental Spatial Analysis collaborates in various
           <a href="http://www.montana.edu/spowell/research.html">
            research grants
           </a>
           .
           <strong>
            <a href="http://landresources.montana.edu/Department/Cooksey.html" target="_blank">
             <br/>
             <br/>
            </a>
           </strong>
          </li>
          <li>
           <a href="http://landresources.montana.edu/dept/faculty/cooksey-d.html">
            <strong>
             Diana Cooksey
            </strong>
           </a>
           is awarded the
           <em>
            President's Award for Excellence in Service Learning
           </em>
           , E-911 Mapping Project.
           <strong>
            <br/>
            <br/>
           </strong>
          </li>
          <li>
           <strong>
            <a href="http://landresources.montana.edu/Department/Lawrence.html">
             Rick Lawrence
            </a>
           </strong>
           , MSU professor and director of the Spatial Sciences Center and
           <a href="http://www.montana.edu/news/12250/msu-part-of-consortium-receiving-10-million-to-investigate-turning-dead-trees-into-biofuel" target="_blank">
            consortium is receiving $10 million to investigate turning dead trees into biofuel.
           </a>
           <br/>
           <br/>
          </li>
          <li>
           <em id="__mceDel">
            <a href="http://www.montana.edu/cpa/news/nwview.php?article=10643" target="_blank">
             Professor
             <strong>
              Rick Lawrence
             </strong>
             and alum
             <strong>
              Shannon Savage
             </strong>
             's geothermal research
            </a>
            in Yellowstone National Park is presented at AGU.
            <br/>
            <br/>
           </em>
          </li>
         </ul>
        </main>
